  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "Which are the most romantic songs in Malayalam?",
  "response": "Here are some of the most romantic songs in Malayalam cinema that have been loved by audiences over the years:\n\n1. **Manassinakkare (from the movie \"Manassinakkare\")**\n   - Composer: M. Jayachandran\n   - Lyricist: Yusuf Ali Kechery\n   - Singer: K. J. Yesudas\n\n2. **Mizhiyil Ninnum (from the movie \"Vaishali\")**\n   - Composer: Bombay Ravi\n   - Lyricist: O. N. V. Kurup\n   - Singer: K. J. Yesudas\n\n3. **Shyamameghame (from the movie \"Nakhakshathangal\")**\n   - Composer: Raveendran\n   - Lyricist: Kaithapram Damodaran Namboothiri\n   - Singer: K. J. Yesudas\n\n4. **Arikil Nee Undayirunnal (from the movie \"Hridayam\")**\n   - Composer: Hesham Abdul Wahab\n   - Lyricist: Kaithapram Damodaran Namboothiri\n   - Singer: Haricharan\n\n5. **Poomaname (from the movie \"Thooval Kottaram\")**\n   - Composer: S. P. Venkatesh\n   - Lyricist: S. Ramesan Nair\n   - Singer: K. S. Chithra\n\n6. **Oru Murai Vanthu (from the movie \"Arikil Oru Veedu\")**\n   - Composer: Ilaiyaraaja\n   - Lyricist: P. Bhaskaran\n   - Singer: K. J. Yesudas\n\n7. **Nee En Sarga Soundaryame (from the movie \"Achuvinte Amma\")**\n   - Composer: Ilaiyaraaja\n   - Lyricist: Gireesh Puthenchery\n   - Singer: K. J. Yesudas\n\n8. **Vennilavu Thenalle (from the movie \"Mayookham\")**\n   - Composer: Raveendran\n   - Lyricist: Kaithapram Damodaran Namboothiri\n   - Singer: P. Jayachandran\n\nThese songs have timeless melodies and beautiful lyrics that capture the essence of romance, making them favorites for many music lovers in Kerala and beyond.",
